This paper deals with improving the compression and fidelity of JPEG images, which involves techniques related to multimedia (cs.MM), computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), graphics (cs.GR), and programming languages (cs.PL). However, since the paper focuses on image compression, the most likely categories are cs.MM and cs.CV, followed by cs.IT, cs.GR, and cs.PL.
